description: With our adorable trucks and mind-blowing Fluff Ice, we're out to bring happiness to all, one cup of Fluff at a time!To learn about the creation of the truck, why it's always good to have friends in the food truck community, and what Fluff Ice means when they say "edible plastic," read Roaming Hunger's blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4581/what-the-fluff
name: The Fluff Ice Truck - OC
